videos.description: Clemson's Khavon Moore reads FSU's pass play perfectly, grabs the steal and takes it to the hoop for a powerful dunk.
videos.headline: Moore turns defense to offense with big dunk

videos.description: M.J. Walker wastes no time in the second half, starting the Seminoles off on the right foot with a deep 3 to tie the game.
videos.headline: Walker shoots from deep to tie the game
